data.name: h_about.Text
data.value:
Connect In Real Time:
Cloudsdale provides reliable realtime communication, around the clock. Free yourself from the old-fashioned way of systematically refreshing the page and receive every single update instantly. We deliver the raw power of the modern web tempered by the grace of good design to you, our beloved users.
Meet New Friends:
Join over 10,000 diverse and interesting people, some of whom may be very similar to you. Cloudsdale is all about embracing the community and allows you to effectively gather as a group. Over time, we've had a lot of people meeting, getting to know each other and performing astounding achievements all while using this service.
Take it with you wherever you go:
Here we want to ensure that you, our users, can rely on always being able to join or bring your friends when you're on the go. We provide beautiful, easy to use mobile applications for the platform of your choice.

data.name: h_message.Text
data.value: Hello, and welcome to Cloudsdale! We hope you enjoy your stay in this city in the clouds. While you're here, be sure to explore some clouds by clicking on the "Explore" button below! All of the information you'll be using here can be access by simply hovering your mouse over the top right corner of the application!
